                            <comment id="13964304" author="sergey_beryozkin" created="Wed, 9 Apr 2014 15:52:39 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;If calling CXF JaxrsUtils.convertFaultToResponse(throwable, currentCxfMessage) returns non-null Response then the exception has been mapped&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13964943" author="njiang" created="Thu, 10 Apr 2014 03:33:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Current CxfRsInvoker just hijack the exception and turn it into WebApplicationException, which disables the CXF default feature of exception mapping. &lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;m working on the patch now.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13965181" author="njiang" created="Thu, 10 Apr 2014 09:52:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Applied the patch into camel master, camel-2.13.x and camel-2.12.x branches.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
